# ==============================================
# SECURITY NOTES
# ==============================================
# 1. NEVER commit this file with real credentials
# 2. Generate secure random strings for all secrets:
#    - Use: openssl rand -hex 32 (for 256-bit keys)
#    - Use: openssl rand -hex 64 (for longer secrets)
# 3. Use different credentials for each environment
# 4. Rotate all secrets regularly
# 5. Use a secure password manager or secret management service
# 6. Enable audit logging for all credential access